# Salesforce Deployment

When deploying to Salesforce, **deploy only changed metadata** instead of the full project:

- Use `npm run deploy:changed` or `./scripts/deploy-changed.sh [target-org]`
- Default target org: `rspca-qld-aosuat`
- The script uses `git diff` to detect changed files and deploys only those components

Full deploy (avoid unless necessary):
- `npm run deploy` or `sf project deploy start --target-org rspca-qld-aosuat`
